{"tid":1678810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 我需要休息但唔會放棄","createTime":"2019-10-28T00:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T09:19:23.000Z","uid":184739,"like":57,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8a5f04a6c76eae80e84b98f44c97a2827abda3","tid":1678810,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:04:31.000Z","msg":"呢4個月冇好好處理自己D情緒不斷發酵,睇新閒睇見手足受傷已經好唔開心,父母又係藍,工作環境大多同事上司都係藍,每日聽到好多唔同既話語罵班手足,琴晚終於開始頂唔順個情緒差D爆煲,有小小處理唔到,咁我雖然有信仰我係基督徒,但琴晚成晚不斷祈禱聽詩歌都無用,最後搵左自己另1個黃絲FD傾下計個先心情先平穩返小小,琴晚成晚就只係諗住想打狗因為真係好嬲心有不甘.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然反送中運動前已經知班狗賊係臭名遠播,反送中開始已經唔係第一次見到班狗日亂拉人亂打人打到班手足流到成地血,但晚晚返到屋企睇返新閒見到有好多手足被捕受傷好心痛呀,我睇左咁多次我都真係唔慣呀 係冇可能慣呀 睇一次嬲一次,行街行到返到屋企已經好攰見到呢D更攰 之前仲可以聽住詩歌都可以比自己個心情平靜到,但琴晚真係feel到唔搵人傾計,點做都無用 今次真係需要休息下 對唔住各位,不過放心,我好快就會出返黎<br />\n<br />\n最後,4個月LA,我知有一班既手足同我都一樣都開始有D攰,個情緒就到達最高點就黎會爆煲,我希望有同我同一樣情況既手足先停一停,比個時間自己靜下先,之後再出黎,因為始終今次運動一定係長期抗爭<br />\n<br />\n再最後 大家記得11月2有集會呀,請準時出席呀!!!! 呢場運動每一個人都好重要 唔好放棄 攰可以停一陣休息下,但唔好放棄呀!!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqYxAve.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqYxAve.jpg&h=3287a369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都一定盡量會出席到,但對唔住 我都應該好快會走,因為真係需要更多私人時間比自己休息<br />\n<br />\n再最後既最後 大家可唔可以比小小支持我,想得多小小溫暖,真係好鬼辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"25c95994e34bacd393afb7298d33a5a6d8730166","tid":1678810,"uid":24027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd61edbdb4f2fe356d5bb8d2baf26a268e1edf8","tid":1678810,"uid":274775,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"加油！<br />\n休息係為左行更遠既路<br />\n互勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a8e755fe4d19f1f1e183ecede6da1ad0bf0d6c","tid":1678810,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:10:08.000Z","msg":"11.2見"},{"pid":"c0cd37e1d2435028b8c16b43fbc6819c33b33837","tid":1678810,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4bPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=ed51ead0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"91adf6442da8b0d302abf4908526fad1e87bea51","tid":1678810,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd61edbdb4f2fe356d5bb8d2baf26a268e1edf8","tid":1678810,"uid":274775,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"加油！<br />\n休息係為左行更遠既路<br />\n互勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:10:29.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58bb1133af457498f2efbf2f4029493d2306627f","tid":1678810,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVceO9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVceO9r.png&h=6fdb41cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0788e44eb2473d3d82f3d396e564d03dd89fabe1","tid":1678810,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58bb1133af457498f2efbf2f4029493d2306627f","tid":1678810,"uid":184739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVceO9r.png